OL,3,CFifteen power cuts in as many days
OL,4,Cleave elderly struggling during cold
OL,5,Csnap
OL,7,FResidents of a road in Bexhill, East
OL,8,FSussex are calling for urgent action
OL,9,Fafter suffering fifteen power cuts in
OL,10,Fas many days.
OL,12,FOlder people living in Green Lane say
OL,13,Flosing their supply has hit them
OL,14,Fparticularly hard during the recent
OL,15,Ffreezing conditions.
OL,17,FThey say over the past two weeks,
OL,18,Fthere have been frequent power cuts
OL,19,Flasting for hours on end.
