OL,7,FUK Power Networks have apologised to
OL,8,Fcustomers and say the power cuts have
OL,9,Fbeen caused by a fault on an
OL,10,Funderground cable.
OL,12,FSomething as simple as boiling a
OL,13,Fkettle has become a bit of a lottery
OL,14,Ffor resident Lynn Webb.
