OL,3,CFifteen power cuts in as many days
OL,4,Cleave elderly struggling during cold
OL,5,Csnap
OL,7,FShe said: "It's been pretty awful
OL,8,Fbecause it's been the coldest week
OL,9,Fwe've had and the heating goes off,
OL,10,Fthe landline goes off. Everything here
OL,11,Fin the house is finished and it's just
OL,12,Fgetting ready, rushing to get a meal
OL,13,Fbefore it goes off again."
OL,15,FAudrey Sneddon lives with a lady who's
OL,16,F100-years-old. They both struggled
OL,17,Fwhen the electricity went off during
OL,18,Fthe night.
