OL,3,CFifteen power cuts in as many days
OL,4,Cleave elderly struggling during cold
OL,5,Csnap
OL,7,F"It was a bit scary really," Audrey
OL,8,Ftold ITV News Meridian. "Pat sleeps
OL,9,Fdownstairs and I had to come down with
OL,10,Fa candle which wasn't easy because I
OL,11,Fcan hardly get down the stairs, it's
OL,12,Fquite a struggle."
OL,14,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for UK
OL,15,FPower Networks said: "UK Power
OL,16,FNetworks apologises to residents in
OL,17,FGreen Lane, Little Common, Bexhill,
OL,18,Ffor recent power cuts which have
OL,19,Fmainly affected 11 customers.
