OL,5,Csnap
OL,7,F"We understand how difficult it is to
OL,8,Fbe without power in such cold weather
OL,9,Fand our team is working to resolve
OL,10,Fthis.
OL,12,F"The power cuts have been caused by a
OL,13,Ffault on an underground cable which
OL,14,Fwill be located and repaired as
OL,15,Fquickly as possible to ensure reliable
OL,16,Fpower supplies in the area.
