OL,4,Cleave elderly struggling during cold
OL,5,Csnap
OL,7,F"As a temporary measure, we have
OL,8,Finstalled equipment enabling us to
OL,9,Fautomatically reconnect power supplies
OL,10,Fquicker, where possible, while work
OL,11,Fcontinues to excavate and repair the
OL,12,Ffault.
OL,14,F"We will be proactively contacting
OL,15,Fcustomers to explain and apologise."
